description:
WARNING!!!!!  Rated -R    REVIVAL and REFORMATION

The purpose of this 7-PART SERIES is to reveal the frightening inroads of SPRITUALISM and its practice that have become deeply embedded within much of the contemporary Seventh-day Adventism.
Using the BIBLE, the SPIRIT OF PROPHECY and HISTORY Evangelist Knott skillfully shows from the stand point of PROPHECY the origin, nature and tendency of this movement and how we can avoid being clutched in its grasp
